12
00:00:38.038 --> 00:00:39.807
- What are you doing?

13
00:00:39.874 --> 00:00:41.509
- [sighs]
I can't sleep.

14
00:00:41.576 --> 00:00:43.377
There's too much honking.

15
00:00:44.311 --> 00:00:46.079
- So close the window.

16
00:00:46.113 --> 00:00:49.383
- The radiators.
It'll get too hot.

17
00:00:49.449 --> 00:00:51.519
- Then turn on
the sound machine.

18
00:00:51.553 --> 00:00:53.721
